{"tid":1383824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真正敵人係呢個腐敗政權","createTime":"2019-07-29T18:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T19:55:14.000Z","uid":235703,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66cbc3a948d5acc9bbe5a500e71128eae0438f40","tid":1383824,"uid":235703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">漸漸地  警隊變成左呢場運動既磨心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n建制派議員、實政圓桌田北辰就元朗襲擊事件去信保安局長李家超，質疑警方未及時處理事件，以及警力安排不當，並要求事件中失職的警隊高層問責辭職。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰在信中要求李家超交代元朗襲擊中警方的處理手法，信中提出6大疑問，包括質疑警方為何未有在接報後立即到場、元朗區助理指揮官游乃強為何於事發當晚稱「同事不見有人持攻擊性武器」，以及何以判斷元朗「風險相對較低」而沒有抽派足夠人手應付事件。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰表示，若未得到警方合理回應，將促請李家超「勒令所有在事件中失職的警隊高層辭職，以承擔責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190726/s00001/1564135058910/%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E3%80%91%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%E4%BF%83%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3-%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%87%89%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190726%2Fs00001%2F1564135058910%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25BE%25B0%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BB%25A3-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=90356c51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190726%2Fs00001%2F1564135058910%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25BE%25B0%25E5%2